<h1> Doctors Show Page </h1><br>

#doctor's name, department, and appointments, with each appointment's date, time, and patient name (linking to the patient's show page). #strftime("%B %-d, %Y at %k:%M")

<h2><%= @doctor.name %> </h2><br>
<h2><%= @doctor.department %> </h2><br>

<% @doctor.appointments.each do |appt| %>
    <%= link_to appt.patient.name, patient_path(appt.patient) %>

    <%= appt.appointment_datetime.strftime("%B %-d, %Y at %k:%M") %>
<% end %>